name: Berswafoto Didepan Mobil Patroli Polisi Yang Terbakar
description:
This illustration tells my imagination about a mass protest that damaged a police patrol car unit and set it on fire, after which I took a selfie in front of the car.

This illustration is done using Chinese ink media on paper and drawing pen with a little digital touch.
